			<h3><span><a class="sharelink" rel="nofollow" href="#p10777" onclick="return false;">Поделиться</a><strong>138</strong><a class="permalink" rel="nofollow" href="http://dekabrist.mybb.ru/viewtopic.php?id=1521&amp;p=14#p10777">06-02-2012 13:51:34</a></span></h3>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="post-author">
